title: Available 2 Bed 2 Bath
posting_body: ['Austin, 78752', 'W St Johns Avenue', '$2225', '2 Bedroom', 'This apartment has hardwood floors in the kitchen, living room, dining room, and the bathroom(s).', 'This unit also has wall-to-wall carpeting in the bedroom(s).', 'The kitchen has granite countertops, all appliances including a dishwasher, and plenty of cabinet space.', 'There is central A/C and heat, patio/balcony, and washer/dryer connections.', 'Unit amenities include tile backsplashes and energy efficient lighting.', 'Select units have a kitchen island with storage, oversized soaking tubs, and stainless steel appliances.', 'Community amenities include fitness center, elevator access, controlled-access community, grilling area, outdoor lounge with fireplace, resort-inspired pool, sunbathing shelf, and a vegetable/herb garden.', 'Pets are welcome.', 'Parking space in a community garage is included with rent there are also reserved parking space options available.', 'Located only a four minute drive to Interstate-35.', 'PHOTOS ARE AN EXAMPLE OF SIMILAR UNITS WITHIN THE BUILDING, ACTUAL UNIT MAY VARY.', '***Availability and pricing is real-time, can change daily, and varies by lease term***', 'Contact Agent:', 'Dave Burroughs', 'Independent Agents Austin TX', 'show contact info', 'Follow us on Twitter @RentalBeast', 'Find us on Facebook: <URL>']
